    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate aggregate RMSE of 0.0042 g/100 L and R² = 0.94 across five operating points, with Pearson r = 0.97, confirming strong model fidelity. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 given the commercial solver, established model forms, and documented team competency. The credibility assessment supports use of the CFD model to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The decision is Accepted.",
